reviewText:
Men on women, women on women...  At least there were no guy/guy scenes.  There was zero plot and really nothing but a bunch of naked people doing what naked people do.  The entire film seems to be under 30 minutes (I am guessing since I fast forwarded through most of it).  I realize it was unrated but goodness gracious it was nothing but a bunch of sex.  I never did figure out much from it other than that the actors and actresses had a lot of enthusiasm for one thing.

I wasted $4.00 including shipping  Please...  there are better alternatives if what this film tried to deliver is what you want.  Horrible grainy picture and I never did understand even a speck if there was a plot.
